cur.execute("INSERT INTO posts (user_id, created, title, subtitle, content) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?)",
            ('1', datetime.now(), "Pee in human's bed", 'Dismember a mouse and then regurgitate parts of it on the family room floor if it smells like fish eat as much as you wish', "<p>Kick up litter you are a captive audience while sitting on the toilet, pet me roll on the floor purring your whiskers off for pet my belly, you know you want to; seize the hand and shred it! hiding behind the couch until lured out by a feathery toy. One of these days i'm going to get that red dot, just you wait and see sleeping in the box. I like to spend my days sleeping and eating fishes that my human fished for me we live on a luxurious yacht, sailing proudly under the sun, i like to walk on the deck, watching the horizon, dreaming of a good bowl of milk hiding behind the couch until lured out by a feathery toy kitty pounce, trip, faceplant you didn't see that no you didn't definitely didn't lick, lick, lick, and preen away the embarrassment jump off balcony, onto stranger's head run as fast as i can into another room for no reason present belly, scratch hand when stroked. Sniff catnip and act crazy fall asleep upside-down. Weigh eight pounds but take up a full-size bed. Fooled again thinking the dog likes me iâ€™m so hungry iâ€™m so hungry but ew not for that but milk the cow thug cat . Brown cats with pink ears. Pet right here, no not there, here, no fool, right here that other cat smells funny you should really give me all the treats because i smell the best and omg you finally got the right spot and i love you right now cough hairball, eat toilet paper yet bathe private parts with tongue then lick owner's face cat dog hate mouse eat string barf pillow no baths hate everything for taco cat backwards spells taco cat intently sniff hand cough furball.</p>"
                                                                                                                                                                                                                     "<p>Try to jump onto window and fall while scratching at wall chase ball of string but fish i must find my red catnip fishy fish yet there's a forty year old lady there let us feast. Allways wanting food hopped up on catnip. Put toy mouse in food bowl run out of litter box at full speed eat the rubberband. Fooled again thinking the dog likes me. Put toy mouse in food bowl run out of litter box at full speed eat prawns daintily with a claw then lick paws clean wash down prawns with a lap of carnation milk then retire to the warmest spot on the couch to claw at the fabric before taking a catnap eat a plant, kill a hand all of a sudden cat goes crazy. I vomit in the bed in the middle of the night furrier and even more furrier hairball carefully drink from water glass and then spill it everywhere and proceed to lick the puddle or chase dog then run away head nudges take a deep sniff of sock then walk around with mouth half open. Drool hunt anything that moves mice. Scratch at door to be let outside, get let out then scratch at door immmediately after to be let back in pee in human's bed until he cleans the litter box. Pounce on unsuspecting person. While happily ignoring when being called eat all the power cords this is the day hell is other people. Hopped up on catnip stare at wall turn and meow stare at wall some more meow again continue staring for sit and stare in the middle of the night i crawl onto your chest and purr gently to help you sleep.</p>"
                                                                                                                                                                                                                     "<p>Chase ball of string i vomit in the bed in the middle of the night, yet lick left leg for ninety minutes, still dirty but have a lot of grump in yourself because you can't forget to be grumpy and not be like king grumpy cat. Good morning sunshine sit as close as possible to warm fire without sitting on cold floor. Catching very fast laser pointer i like big cats and i can not lie and hiiiiiiiiii feed me now wack the mini furry mouse but naughty running cat. Lie on your belly and purr when you are asleep. Hide from vacuum cleaner give attitude i is not fat, i is fluffy this human feeds me, i should be a god. Rub face on owner mark territory, so run outside as soon as door open but curl into a furry donut. Lick face hiss at owner, pee a lot, and meow repeatedly scratch at fence purrrrrr eat muffins and poutine until owner comes back litter kitter kitty litty little kitten big roar roar feed me or sleep nap for get scared by doggo also cucumerro or run up and down stairs for i heard this rumor where the humans are our owners, pfft, what do they know?! eat the rubberband. Cat meoooow i iz master of hoomaan, not hoomaan master of i, oooh damn dat dog reaches under door into adjacent room or cat dog hate mouse eat string barf pillow no baths hate everything mesmerizing birds. Experiences short bursts of poo-phoria after going to the loo stinky cat favor packaging over toy but kitty kitty pussy cat doll attempt to leap between furniture but woefully miscalibrate and bellyflop onto the floor; what's your problem? i meant to do that now i shall wash myself intently for pelt around the house and up and down stairs chasing phantoms. Making sure that fluff gets into the owner's eyes sit on human they not getting up ever. Lick the curtain just to be annoying. Ask for petting i bet my nine lives on you-oooo-ooo-hooo or meowsiers, fight own tail yet hunt anything that moves, or cats are the world. I am the best being gorgeous with belly side up, kitty run to human with blood on mouth from frenzied attack on poor innocent mouse, don't i look cute? yet swat turds around the house lick butt. Peer out window, chatter at birds, lure them to mouth murr i hate humans they are so annoying.</p>")
            )

cur.execute("INSERT INTO posts (user_id, created, title, subtitle, content) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?)",
            ('2', datetime.now(), "Find empty spot in cupboard and sleep all day", 'Fight own tail human give me attention meow yet somehow manage to catch a bird but have no idea what to do next', "<p>Cat ipsum dolor sit amet, you have cat to be kitten me right meow and eat a plant, kill a hand, yet jump off balcony, onto stranger's head, and cuddle no cuddle cuddle love scratch scratch. What the heck just happened, something feels fishy proudly present butt to human. Chew foot lick face hiss at owner, pee a lot, and meow repeatedly scratch at fence purrrrrr eat muffins and poutine until owner comes back but my cat stared at me he was sipping his tea, too and i rule on my back you rub my tummy i bite you hard for cough hairball, eat toilet paper get my claw stuck in the dog's ear. Has closed eyes but still sees you stuff and things and get poop stuck in paws jumping out of litter box and run around the house scream meowing and smearing hot cat mud all over claws in the eye of the beholder.</p>"
                                                                                                                                                                                                                     "<p>Meowsiers cats are a queer kind of folk sleep nap, immediately regret falling into bathtub. Leave hair on owner's clothes chew foot good morning sunshine for thug cat with tail in the air. Car rides are evil steal mom's crouton while she is in the bathroom but eat the rubberband so i'm bored inside, let me out i'm lonely outside, let me in i can't make up my mind whether to go in or out, guess i'll just stand partway in and partway out, contemplating the universe for half an hour how dare you nudge me with your foot?!?! leap into the air in greatest offense!. Cereal boxes make for five star accommodation groom forever, stretch tongue and leave it slightly out, blep, so lick the plastic bag do i like standing on litter cuz i sits when i have spaces, my cat buddies have no litter i live in luxury cat life avoid the new toy and just play with the box it came in, poop on couch. Enslave the hooman walk on a keyboard. Man running from cops stops to pet cats, goes to jail jumps off balcony gives owner dead mouse at present then poops in litter box snatches yarn and fights with dog cat chases laser then plays in grass finds tiny spot in cupboard and sleeps all day jumps in bathtub and meows when owner fills food dish the cat knocks over the food dish cat slides down the water slide and into pool and swims even though it does not like water for murr i hate humans they are so annoying, and annoy the old grumpy cat, start a fight and then retreat to wash when i lose yet meowing chowing and wowing for tweeting a baseball cat cat moo moo lick ears lick paws.</p>"
                                                                                                                                                                                                                     "<p>Catch small lizards, bring them into house, then unable to find them on carpet hit you unexpectedly scratch my tummy actually i hate you now fight me so if human is on laptop sit on the keyboard. Don't nosh on the birds purrr purr littel cat, little cat purr purr i like to spend my days sleeping and eating fishes that my human fished for me we live on a luxurious yacht, sailing proudly under the sun, i like to walk on the deck, watching the horizon, dreaming of a good bowl of milk for purr for no reason but nap all day.</p>")
            )

